.TH "lingmo-reader" "1" "2021-1-28" "Lingmo"
.SH NAME
lingmo-reader
.SH DESCRIPTION
a tool for reading document files,supporting PDF, DJVU, DOCX etc
.SH SYNOPSIS
lingmo-reader [FILE(s)...] [OPTIONS...]
.SH OPTIONS
.PP
-thumbnail    tell lingmo-reader to generate thumbnail of PDF file
.PP
-f -filePath    thumbnail source file,this option needs to be set after -thumbnail
.PP
-t -thumbnailPath    thumbnail generation path,this option needs to be set after -thumbnail
.SH SEE ALSO
https://github.com/lingmoos/lingmo-reader
.SH AUTHOR
